  <scopecontent id="aspace_ae1dee21785b18de1b4f6efa8155dfa4">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence; diary, 1926-1940; clippings; addresses; speeches; journals; pamphlets; and notes of Mary Beard. Collection consists primarily of diary entries recording job related activities; speeches concern public health and nursing issues.</p>  </scopecontent>
